I went in and ordered my regular iced caramel latte with cream and whipped cream. First of all, it looked like a cup of milk with caramel at the bottom. When I told the guy, who I assume to be the manager, he argued with me telling me because i ordered with cream it’s going to be that light. I’ve been ordering this drink for YEARS primarily from this location which was previously managed by someone else and I’ve NEVER had this issue. He didn’t offer to remake it, instead he decided to pour cream in a cup with ice to show me that “the cream is too heavy” and another customer thought it was a little absurd. The drink was absolutely disgusting and served no purpose. I simply just threw the drink in the garbage. Thanks for ruining my morning and taking my money :) but after being a valued customer for over 5 years at this location you will NOT be getting my business any longer.
